Alone:                                                                                                           

                                                                                                         
Why does it hurt when you feel all alone, Cutting in deep straight through the bone? Surrounded by darkness and feeling so cold, Wanting to touch when there's no one to hold, Wanting to talk when there's no one to hear, Alone in the dark drowning with fear. Why does it hurt when you feel all alone, Taken from the warm feelings you once had known? Misery is the only company you got for when you feel alone you feel it a lot.</LABEL>
